    "For example, extracting names of people, organizations, and locations from news articles or social media posts [40], [41], [42], [43], [44].",
    "(b) Question Answering Systems: Named Entity Recognition helps in identifying entities mentioned in a question and linking them to relevant information in a knowledge base.",
